exceptions.exn: In environment i, k, n : nat v : vec nat n H1 : divides (ps i) (exp 0 (snd (k, v))) H : nat Unable to unify "nat" with "divides (ps k) (exp i v)".

original: intros H. unfold encode_state in H. simpl fst in H. apply divides_mult_inv in H as [H1|H1]. - apply primestream_divides in H1. auto. - exfalso. apply (ps_exp k v i). apply H1.
